    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, pick the<strong> basil leaves</strong> from their stalks and discard the stalks&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>\r\n<p>Grind 1/2 tsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [1 tsp]</span> <strong>black pepper</strong> into a small bowl&nbsp;</p>",
