    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chicken thighs</strong>,&nbsp;<strong>ground cumin</strong>, <strong>ground coriander</strong>, <strong>paprika</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and half the<strong> cayenne pepper&nbsp;</strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>apple&nbsp;cider vinegar</strong>,&nbsp;a generous pinch of<strong> salt&nbsp;</strong>and give everything a good stir</p>\r\n<p>Reduce the heat to low and cook, covered, for 20 min or until the chicken is cooked and coated in the sauce&nbsp;- this is your <strong>chicken vindaloo</strong></p>",
