    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the<strong> green beans</strong> in half&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Heat a small pot with a matching lid over a medium-high heat&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the<strong> chopped green beans</strong> with a splash of <strong>water</strong> and cook, covered, for 3 min or until they're tender</p>\r\n<p>Once tender, remove the lid and cook for a further 1-2 min or until all of the water has evaporated</p>",
