    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the<strong> mini coriander naans</strong> to a baking tray&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Put the tray in the oven for 3 min or until they're warmed through&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Once done, remove the <strong>naans</strong> from the oven and wrap them in a tea towel to keep warm until serving</p>",
