    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the <strong>water</strong>&nbsp;has evaporated from the green&nbsp;beans, reduce the heat to medium-low</p>\r\n<p>Add&nbsp;a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and the remaining <strong>yellow mustard seeds</strong> and cook for 1 min or until they&nbsp;begin to pop</p>\r\n<p>Remove the pan from the heat, season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and the remaining <strong>cayenne pepper</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) - these are your <strong>spiced&nbsp;green beans</strong></p>",
