      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> chicken vindaloo</strong> over the<strong> basmati rice</strong> with the<strong>&nbsp;spiced green beans</strong>,&nbsp;<strong>G</strong><strong>reek-style yoghurt</strong> and <strong>warm</strong><strong>&nbsp;naan</strong>&nbsp;to the side&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Enjoy!&nbsp;</p>",
